  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0dc0\u0ddb\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4-\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca-\u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda-\u0daf\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db3\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3:\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0d9c\u0dd3\u0dc4\u0dd4-\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda-\u0daf\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca-\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db3\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2/101-615540",
  "time_ut": 1656401303,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0ddb\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0daf\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db3\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3:\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0d9c\u0dd3\u0dc4\u0dd4 \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda \u0daf\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db3\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "When doctors suffer in the oil queue: Patients suffer in the hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nikaweratiya hospital staff including doctors were waiting in line for fuel.",
        "The hospital staff said that their vehicles were currently running out of fuel on the highway and demanded that immediate fuel be provided to continue the treatment of thousands of patients.",
        "The hospital staff said that the situation had arisen due to the lack of a proper system to dispense fuel to them at petrol stations and that this had caused severe injustice to the patients as well.",
        "A hospital spokesman said only the hospital's essential care services were operational. The spokesman further stated that this situation has arisen due to the non-supply of fuel to the staff to maintain the hospital operations.",
        "Outpatients at the hospital were paralyzed and returning for outpatient treatment."
      ],
